5d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0273.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0273.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0273.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2mh6-5954-wmgr/GHSA-2mh6-5954-wmgr.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/sunkill.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0273.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82086/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0459.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0424","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0424.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0239","title":"Netscape FastTrack Server 目录列表信息泄露漏洞","description":"tags.<value>Netscape FastTrack Server 3.0.1 存在目录列表漏洞，由于服务器对 HTTP 方法的大小写处理不当，攻击者使用小写的 \"get\" 命令替代标准的大写 \"GET\" 发送请求时，服务器会返回根目录及子目录的文件列表，导致敏感信息泄露。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用此漏洞遍历服务器文件系统，获取配置文件、源代码等敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Netscape FastTrack Server 3.0.1 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0239"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.770","remediation":"Netscape FastTrack Server 3.0.1 已停止维护超过二十年，官方不再提供安全补丁。建议立即迁移至仍受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx 或 Microsoft IIS）。若短期内无法迁移，可在反向代理或 WAF 层面配置规则拦截小写 HTTP 方法（将小写 get 请求转换为 400/403 响应）作为临时缓解措施，同时严格限制可访问该服务器的源 IP 范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/122","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1731","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19363","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0239.json","https://github.com/kenhuangus/llm-wiki/blob/d2bd485921f6c7b6071afbb389f44ab8e4e83c69/wiki/security/cve/cve-1999-0239.md","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0239","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0239.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0239.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vcjq-7hcj-xh74/GHSA-vcjq-7hcj-xh74.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/netscape_fasttrack.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_100_200.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0424.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0424.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0424.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0257","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0257.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0114","title":"Elm elm-2.4 邮件系统本地符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Elm-2.4 邮件客户端中的 filter 命令存在符号链接（symlink）攻击漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在临时目录中创建恶意符号链接，诱使 filter 命令以其他用户的权限执行任意命令或读取敏感文件。该漏洞利用条件为拥有本地账户权限，影响范围包括使用 Elm-2.4 的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级到不受影响的版本或禁用 filter 功能。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0114"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.097","remediation":"立即升级至 Elm 2.4 Patch Level 3 及以上版本，该版本修复了 filter 命令在处理临时文件时的竞态条件问题。若无法升级，建议禁用 filter 命令或移除 elm 的 setuid 权限位以限制 symlink 攻击。长期建议迁移至 mutt 或 alpine 等持续维护的邮件客户端。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0114"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0257.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0242","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0242.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0107","title":"Apache HTTP Server 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache 1.2.5 及更早版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送大量包含大量 `/` 字符的恶意 GET 请求触发此漏洞，导致 Apache 服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Apache 1.2.5 及之前所有版本，攻击无需身份认证，利用难度较低，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0107"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.150","remediation":"建议升级至 Apache 1.3.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复超大 GET 请求导致的缓冲区溢出。如无法升级，可在反向代理层（如 Nginx）限制单个 URI 长度不超过 4096 字节，并在 Web 应用防火墙中配置请求速率限制以缓解 DDoS 风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0107","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20558","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0107.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0107.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0107","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-